          <Comment>For these reasons, this variant has been classified as Pathogenic. ClinVar contains an entry for this variant (Variation ID: 958387). This variant has not been reported in the literature in individuals affected with ALDH7A1-related conditions. This variant is not present in population databases (gnomAD no frequency). This sequence change creates a premature translational stop signal (p.Thr31Serfs*25) in the ALDH7A1 gene. It is expected to result in an absent or disrupted protein product. Loss-of-function variants in ALDH7A1 are known to be pathogenic (PMID: 16491085, 20554659).</Comment>
